## Formulas implemented

```
Max Allowable MW (C)  =  MWT  +  FST / (Shoe TVD × 0.052)
                         → round DOWN to 1 decimal place

Initial MAASP         =  [(C) − Current MW]  ×  Shoe TVD  ×  0.052
                         → round DOWN to whole number (psi)

Kill Mud Weight       =  Current MW  +  SIDPP / (Hole TVD × 0.052)
                         → round UP to 1 decimal place

ICP                   =  Dynamic Pressure Loss  +  SIDPP

FCP                   =  (KMW / Current MW)  ×  DPL

K / 100 strokes       =  (ICP − FCP) / DS Total Strokes  ×  100

Volume (bbl)          =  Length (ft)  ×  Capacity (bbl/ft)

Pump Strokes          =  Volume / Pump Displacement          → ceiling integer

Time (min)            =  Strokes / SPM                       → ceiling integer
```

