## File structure

Everything lives in a single file — **`surface_kill_sheet_screen.dart`**:

```
SurfaceKillSheetData          — immutable const data model; every PDF field in one object
PDF colour constants           — PdfColors aliases used across all section builders
PDF font globals               — _regular, _bold, _italic, _boldItalic (loaded once)
_sT()                         — central TextStyle factory for PDF text
PDF primitive helpers          — _box(), _boxNoBorder(), _underline() etc.
PDF section builders:
  _buildHeader()              — IWCF title + date/name underlines
  _buildFormationBlock()      — Formation Strength + MAASP formula layout
  _buildPumpBlock()           — Pump displacement + slow-pump rate table
  _buildRightPanel()          — Current Well Data column + well schematic image
  _buildVolumeTable()         — Pre-recorded volume data table (DS, OH, annulus)
  _buildKillSheetPage2()      — Full page 2 (kick data through graph section)
generateSurfaceKillSheetPdf() — assembles both pages, loads fonts/image, returns bytes
SurfaceKillSheetScreen        — StatefulWidget; the Navigator push target
_SurfaceKillSheetScreenState  — all TextEditingControllers, computed strings,
                                 _recalcAll(), save/load, export, 7 section builders
_WellDiagramPainter           — CustomPainter: live well schematic
_StepDownChartPainter         — CustomPainter: pressure step-down graph
_InlineDatePicker             — OverlayEntry calendar dropdown anchored to date field
_InlineExportMenu             — OverlayEntry PDF action menu (download / print / share)
_SlotPickerDialog             — modal dialog: 5-slot grid for save or open
_SlotLabelDialog              — modal dialog: name-entry before saving a slot
```

